{"title":"第三周课程-SQL与PHP","uid":"bcd80a5ebbb48bb852bbee5672f0a5b3","slug":"第三周课程-SQL与PHP","date":"2024-02-01T07:08:19.000Z","updated":"2024-02-02T03:36:44.144Z","comments":true,"path":"api/articles/第三周课程-SQL与PHP.json","keywords":null,"cover":[],"content":"<h2 id=\"MySQL基本操作\"><a href=\"#MySQL基本操作\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"MySQL基本操作\"></a>MySQL基本操作</h2><div class=\"language-txt\"><button title=\"Copy code\" class=\"copy\"></button><span class=\"lang\">txt</span><pre class=\"shiki material-theme-palenight\" style=\"background-color: #1a1a1a\" tabindex=\"0\"><code><span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #babed8\">-- 创建数据库</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #babed8\">CREATE DATABASE 数据库名;</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #babed8\"></span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #babed8\">-- 选择数据库</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #babed8\">USE 数据库名;</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #babed8\"></span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #babed8\">-- 创建表格</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #babed8\">CREATE TABLE 表格名 (</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #babed8\">    列1 数据类型,</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #babed8\">    列2 数据类型,</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #babed8\">    ...</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #babed8\">);</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #babed8\"></span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #babed8\">-- 插入数据</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #babed8\">INSERT INTO 表格名 (列1, 列2, ...)</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #babed8\">VALUES (值1, 值2, ...);</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #babed8\"></span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #babed8\">-- 查询数据</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #babed8\">SELECT 列1, 列2, ...</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #babed8\">FROM 表格名</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #babed8\">WHERE 条件;</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #babed8\"></span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #babed8\">-- 更新数据</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #babed8\">UPDATE 表格名</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #babed8\">SET 列1 = 值1, 列2 = 值2, ...</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #babed8\">WHERE 条件;</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #babed8\"></span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #babed8\">-- 删除数据</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #babed8\">DELETE FROM 表格名</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #babed8\">WHERE 条件;</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #babed8\"></span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #babed8\">-- 删除表格</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #babed8\">DROP TABLE 表格名;</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #babed8\"></span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #babed8\">-- 删除数据库</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #babed8\">DROP DATABASE 数据库名;</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #babed8\"></span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #babed8\">-- 修改表格结构（添加列）</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #babed8\">ALTER TABLE 表格名</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #babed8\">ADD COLUMN 新列 数据类型;</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #babed8\"></span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #babed8\">-- 修改表格结构（修改列）</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #babed8\">ALTER TABLE 表格名</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #babed8\">MODIFY COLUMN 列名 数据类型;</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #babed8\"></span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #babed8\">-- 修改表格结构（删除列）</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #babed8\">ALTER TABLE 表格名</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #babed8\">DROP COLUMN 列名;</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #babed8\"></span></span></code></pre></div><p>ORDER BY 字句，排列语句：</p>\n<div class=\"language-txt\"><button title=\"Copy code\" class=\"copy\"></button><span class=\"lang\">txt</span><pre class=\"shiki material-theme-palenight\" style=\"background-color: #1a1a1a\" tabindex=\"0\"><code><span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #babed8\">SELECT *或其他 FROM 数据表(可以是多个) ORDER BY 字段 ASC/DESC;</span></span></code></pre></div><p><code>ASC</code>是升序排序，<code>DESC</code>是降序排序。     </p>\n<p>我们可以使用数字来进行判断列长度，比如： </p>\n<p>![](D:&#x2F;WeChat Files&#x2F;wxid_pv4vlb3mg6mv22&#x2F;FileStorage&#x2F;File&#x2F;2024-02&#x2F;image&#x2F;判断列的长度.jpg) </p>\n<p>观察不同点在哪</p>\n<p>UNION字句，联合查询</p>\n<p>所谓联合查询，就是查询不同的两个表，将要查询的信息合并显示。<br>联合查询有两个子句：<br><code>UNION 子句</code>：查询后不显示重复数据<br><code>UNION ALL 子句</code>：查询后会显示重复数据            </p>\n<div class=\"language-txt\"><button title=\"Copy code\" class=\"copy\"></button><span class=\"lang\">txt</span><pre class=\"shiki material-theme-palenight\" style=\"background-color: #1a1a1a\" tabindex=\"0\"><code><span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #babed8\">SELECT (*或其他) FROM 数据表1 UNION SELECT (*或其他) FROM 数据表2；</span></span></code></pre></div><p>![](D:&#x2F;WeChat Files&#x2F;wxid_pv4vlb3mg6mv22&#x2F;FileStorage&#x2F;File&#x2F;2024-02&#x2F;image&#x2F;联合查询.jpg)</p>\n<h2 id=\"MySQL其他知识点\"><a href=\"#MySQL其他知识点\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"MySQL其他知识点\"></a>MySQL其他知识点</h2><p>1、MySQL的注释：<code>#从这开始到后面都是注释</code>，<code>--从这开始到后面都是注释</code>，<code>/*这全是注释*/</code><br>2、常见的内置函数</p>\n<div class=\"language-txt\"><button title=\"Copy code\" class=\"copy\"></button><span class=\"lang\">txt</span><pre class=\"shiki material-theme-palenight\" style=\"background-color: #1a1a1a\" tabindex=\"0\"><code><span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #babed8\">database() : 显示当前数据库名称</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #babed8\">current_user ： 显示当前用户</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #babed8\">version() : 显示当前数据库版本</span></span></code></pre></div><p>![](D:&#x2F;WeChat Files&#x2F;wxid_pv4vlb3mg6mv22&#x2F;FileStorage&#x2F;File&#x2F;2024-02&#x2F;image&#x2F;内置函数.png)</p>\n<h2 id=\"PHP基础\"><a href=\"#PHP基础\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"PHP基础\"></a>PHP基础</h2><h4 id=\"说明\"><a href=\"#说明\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"说明\"></a>说明</h4><ul>\n<li><p>全称”超文本预处理器”</p>\n</li>\n<li><p>PHP在WEB中充当中间人的角色，它主要处理WEB数据</p>\n</li>\n<li><p>PHP的工作流程:<br><img src=\"https://i0.imgs.ovh/2024/02/01/KqpnT.png\"></p>\n</li>\n<li><p>学习: <a href=\"https://www.w3schools.com/PHP/php_exercises.asp\">PHP Exercise</a></p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<h3 id=\"基本语法\"><a href=\"#基本语法\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"基本语法\"></a>基本语法</h3><h4 id=\"变量\"><a href=\"#变量\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"变量\"></a>变量</h4><ul>\n<li>以 <code>$</code>开头, 如<code>$_a</code></li>\n<li>大小写敏感</li>\n</ul>\n<h5 id=\"服务器变量\"><a href=\"#服务器变量\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"服务器变量\"></a>服务器变量</h5><ul>\n<li><p><code>$_SERVER</code>包含服务器和执行环境的信息</p>\n</li>\n<li><p><code>_ENV</code>包含环境变量的信息</p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n","feature":true,"text":"MySQL基本操作txt-- 创建数据库 CREATE DATABASE 数据库名; -- 选择数据库 USE 数据库名; -- 创建表格 CREATE TAB...","permalink":"/post/第三周课程-SQL与PHP","photos":[],"count_time":{"symbolsCount":"1.5k","symbolsTime":"1 mins."},"categories":[],"tags":[{"name":"网络安全","slug":"网络安全","count":10,"path":"api/tags/网络安全.json"},{"name":"SQL基础","slug":"SQL基础","count":2,"path":"api/tags/SQL基础.json"},{"name":"学习日志","slug":"学习日志","count":10,"path":"api/tags/学习日志.json"},{"name":"视频会议","slug":"视频会议","count":3,"path":"api/tags/视频会议.json"}],"toc":"<ol class=\"toc\"><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-2\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#MySQL%E5%9F%BA%E6%9C%AC%E6%93%8D%E4